<div id="review_3082153666" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3082153666" />
    <a title="Ed" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1077703-ed"><img alt="Ed" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1626131115p2/1077703.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3082153666?book_show_action=true">Dec 16, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ed" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ed" href="/user/show/1077703-ed">Ed</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3082153666" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14167331098447676407">Many years ago, I attended a Maya Angelou reading and afterwards, she signed one of her books for me. A lovely lady, she was outgoing and gracious. This memoir covers her early 30s. She meets and works for historical icons like Billie Holiday and MLK. I was surprised to learn some things about her I didn&apos;t know before, but I won&apos;t play spoiler and recount them here. She certainly had more than her share of heartbreaks and challenges. I thoroughly enjoyed the read. </span>
  <span id="freeText14167331098447676407" style="display:none">Many years ago, I attended a Maya Angelou reading and afterwards, she signed one of her books for me. A lovely lady, she was outgoing and gracious. This memoir covers her early 30s. She meets and works for historical icons like Billie Holiday and MLK. I was surprised to learn some things about her I didn't know before, but I won't play spoiler and recount them here. She certainly had more than her share of heartbreaks and challenges. I thoroughly enjoyed the read. </span>
