<div id="review_1723451020" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1723451020" />
    <a title="Joanna" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/620387-joanna"><img alt="Joanna" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1195069470p2/620387.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1723451020?book_show_action=true">Aug 09, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joanna" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joanna" href="/user/show/620387-joanna">Joanna</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/6493830-the-heart-of-a-woman">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/620387-joanna?shelf=nonfiction">nonfiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/620387-joanna?shelf=2016-read">2016-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/620387-joanna?shelf=rws-2016-summer">rws-2016-summer</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/620387-joanna?shelf=kindle">kindle</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/620387-joanna?shelf=biography-memoir">biography-memoir</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1723451020" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16425311383109846104">Absolutely gripping, fabulously written, heartbreakingly honest. This book grabbed me by the throat and held on. Angelou lived in interesting times and writes about both personal and societal turmoil. She makes her experiences accessible and does not flinch from the difficulties that she faced (and overcame). Cameo appearances by famous people felt like a cool scene in a movie rather than mere name dropping. Watch for James Earl Jones, James Baldwin, plus meetings with Martin Luther King, Jr., a</span>
  <span id="freeText16425311383109846104" style="display:none">Absolutely gripping, fabulously written, heartbreakingly honest. This book grabbed me by the throat and held on. Angelou lived in interesting times and writes about both personal and societal turmoil. She makes her experiences accessible and does not flinch from the difficulties that she faced (and overcame). Cameo appearances by famous people felt like a cool scene in a movie rather than mere name dropping. Watch for James Earl Jones, James Baldwin, plus meetings with Martin Luther King, Jr., and Malcolm X. Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16425311383109846104" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


